        <section id="research" class="section">
            <h2>Current Research Project</h2>
            <h3>TAXMORALBIAS – Tax Morale and Social Desirability Bias: Examining the Shadow Economy Experimentally</h3>
            <p>Grant authority: European Commission Marie Skłodowska-Curie Actions<br>
            Total budget: €172,750.08<br>
            Project leader at Collegio Carlo Alberto</p>
            <p>This project explores how tax morale influences social desirability bias, aiming to reduce the size of the shadow economy by implementing and combining list, vignette and field experiments.</p>
        </section>

